 the screen capture, a screenshot with a reference signing view is prepared in the Scrive e-signing system at each production upgrade. Upon sealing the document, the Scrive e-signing system includes the latest reference signing view in this Evidence of Intent (one per party that signed). The reference signing view is included as a reference even if the screen capture succeeded.</p><p>Important to note is also that, in the event log below each time stamp reflects the clock of the client, and may be different from the server clock.</p><p>$EvidenceOfIntentTable()$</p></body></html>
